<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>يس <span class="c2">(١)</span> وَالْقُرْآنِ الْحَكِيمِ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> إِنَّكَ لَمِنَ الْمُرْسَلِينَ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> عَلَى صِرَاطٍ مُسْتَقِيمٍ <span class="c2">(٤)</span> تَنْزِيلَ الْعَزِيزِ الرَّحِيمِ <span class="c2">(٥)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>